# drawing a barchart 

Univariate distribution: overall happiness levels


```r
ggplot(data = happy, aes(x = happy)) + geom_bar()
```

![](learning-community-nov-7_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png)&lt;!-- --&gt;


